    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A clear, colorless, poisonous liquid which can be polymerized to form acrylic and modacrylic fibers. It is coplymerized with butadiene to create nitrile rubber. Acrylonitrile is also used as an insecticide.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
